Revision history for OpenInteract package base_error.

3.02  Mon Feb 28 20:33:57 EST 2005

      OIN-72: move docs from doc/ into OI2::App class

3.01  Sun Feb 27 16:07:21 EST 2005

      OIN-137: change package.conf -> package.ini

3.00  Wed Feb 23 22:00:46 EST 2005

      OIN-35: Revamp package to store errors in filesystem instead of
      database. (Initial version with lots of small iterations....)

2.10  Thu Feb 19 09:51:38 EST 2004

      Modify the 'message' field to be 'err_message' ('message' is a
      reserved word in t-sql) and add field_map to the SPOPS object
      so that referencing 'message' still works.

2.09  ... no label!

      - Cosmetic...

2.08  Wed Nov 19 23:23:52 EST 2003

      OI2::ErrorObject subclasses persistence implementation
      generated by SPOPS.

2.07  Mon Oct 13 19:12:21 EDT 2003

      Add note in OI2::SQLInstall::Error about data migration.

2.06  Fri Sep  5 10:30:40 EDT 2003

      Doc updates, small.

2.05  Sat Aug 30 12:40:07 EDT 2003

      Modify use of 'row_color' template widget.

2.04  Fri Jun 27 02:20:19 EDT 2003

      Changed schema of sys_error table and matched it with action
      and template changes.

2.03  Wed Jun 25 10:29:24 EDT 2003

      Lots of intervening changes; update to use log4p

2.02  Mon Mar 31 21:32:16 EST 2003

      Translate conf/spops.perl into INI format; other small changes.

2.01  Sat Mar 22 12:59:44 EST 2003

      Use new OI.make_url syntax, and add form_button TT calls to
      search results.

2.00  Thu Mar 20 11:40:31 EST 2003

      Initial changes for OI2.

1.45  Mon Feb 17 11:12:58 EST 2003

      Remove template/error_display.tmpl since it duplicates the
      site-wide template 'error_message'; update package docs.

1.44  Mon Jan  6 22:46:33 EST 2003

      Change all 'datetime' datatypes to use the '%%DATETIME%%' key.

1.43  Sun Aug 25 11:45:20 EDT 2002

      Remove all template/*.meta files.

1.42  Thu May  2 09:20:00 EDT 2002

      Add Interbase-specific table

1.41  Tue Apr 16 15:00:30 EDT 2002

      Change 'datetime' -> 'date' in struct/sys_error_oracle.sql

1.40  Mon Apr  1 21:17:36 EST 2002

      Add Oracle-specific tables; rename structure files to match
      table names.

